Google Sheets Clone
A web-based spreadsheet application inspired by Google Sheets, built using React, Handsontable, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB. This project allows users to create, edit, and save spreadsheets with support for formulas.

ğŸš€ Features
âœ… Handsontable-based spreadsheet UI
âœ… Save and load spreadsheets to/from MongoDB
âœ… Supports basic formulas like SUM, AVERAGE, MAX, MIN, COUNT, etc.
âœ… Text transformation functions: TRIM, UPPER, LOWER, FIND_AND_REPLACE
âœ… Remove duplicate values in a range
âœ… Dynamic cell calculations

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack
Frontend: React.js, Handsontable, Axios
Backend: Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, Mongoose
